### 1. MCP 토큰 발급 — shopper-llm
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientId": "shopper-llm",
  "clientSecret": "dev-secret-1"
}

### 2. MCP 토큰 발급 — catalog-only-llm
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientId": "catalog-only-llm",
  "clientSecret": "dev-secret-2"
}

### 3. MCP 토큰 발급 — ops-llm
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientId": "ops-llm",
  "clientSecret": "dev-secret-3"
}

### 4. 잘못된 자격증명 → 401
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientId": "shopper-llm",
  "clientSecret": "WRONG_SECRET"
}


### 5. /sse — 토큰 없이 호출 시 401
GET http://localhost:8080/sse
Accept: text/event-stream

### 6. /sse — 잘못된 토큰 → 401
GET http://localhost:8080/sse
Accept: text/event-stream
Authorization: Bearer invalid.token.value

### 7. /sse — 정상 토큰 (응답 첫 줄의 sessionId 를 복사해 아래 #8~#11 의 ?sessionId=... 에 붙여넣기)
GET http://localhost:8080/sse
Accept: text/event-stream
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJzaG9wcGVyLWxsbSIsImlzcyI6ImNsb3RoaW5nLWVjb21tZXJjZS1tY3AiLCJpYXQiOjE3Nzk2OTQ2MTEsImV4cCI6MTc3OTY5ODIxMSwic2NvcGVzIjoiY2F0YWxvZzpyZWFkIG9yZGVyOnJlYWQgb3JkZXI6d3JpdGUifQ.GUGuavEK1uB8W4KMixbZXAepNkeR7q_I8BjsYQzQKEQ


### 8. MCP initialize — 첫 핸드셰이크 (sessionId 는 #7 응답에서 복사)
POST http://localhost:8080/mcp/message?sessionId=PASTE_SESSION_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJzaG9wcGVyLWxsbSIsImlzcyI6ImNsb3RoaW5nLWVjb21tZXJjZS1tY3AiLCJpYXQiOjE3Nzk2OTQ2MTEsImV4cCI6MTc3OTY5ODIxMSwic2NvcGVzIjoiY2F0YWxvZzpyZWFkIG9yZGVyOnJlYWQgb3JkZXI6d3JpdGUifQ.GUGuavEK1uB8W4KMixbZXAepNkeR7q_I8BjsYQzQKEQ

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 1,
  "method": "initialize",
  "params": {
    "protocolVersion": "2024-11-05",
    "capabilities": {},
    "clientInfo": { "name": "http-client", "version": "1.0" }
  }
}

### 9. MCP notifications/initialized — 초기화 완료 통보 (이거 안 보내면 tools/list 가 응답 안 함)
POST http://localhost:8080/mcp/message?sessionId=PASTE_SESSION_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJzaG9wcGVyLWxsbSIsImlzcyI6ImNsb3RoaW5nLWVjb21tZXJjZS1tY3AiLCJpYXQiOjE3Nzk2OTQ2MTEsImV4cCI6MTc3OTY5ODIxMSwic2NvcGVzIjoiY2F0YWxvZzpyZWFkIG9yZGVyOnJlYWQgb3JkZXI6d3JpdGUifQ.GUGuavEK1uB8W4KMixbZXAepNkeR7q_I8BjsYQzQKEQ

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "notifications/initialized"
}

### 10. MCP tools/list — 노출된 도구 목록 조회
POST http://localhost:8080/mcp/message?sessionId=PASTE_SESSION_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJzaG9wcGVyLWxsbSIsImlzcyI6ImNsb3RoaW5nLWVjb21tZXJjZS1tY3AiLCJpYXQiOjE3Nzk2OTQ2MTEsImV4cCI6MTc3OTY5ODIxMSwic2NvcGVzIjoiY2F0YWxvZzpyZWFkIG9yZGVyOnJlYWQgb3JkZXI6d3JpdGUifQ.GUGuavEK1uB8W4KMixbZXAepNkeR7q_I8BjsYQzQKEQ

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 2,
  "method": "tools/list"
}

### 11. MCP tools/call — 도구 실제 호출 (searchProducts)
POST http://localhost:8080/mcp/message?sessionId=PASTE_SESSION_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJzaG9wcGVyLWxsbSIsImlzcyI6ImNsb3RoaW5nLWVjb21tZXJjZS1tY3AiLCJpYXQiOjE3Nzk2OTQ2MTEsImV4cCI6MTc3OTY5ODIxMSwic2NvcGVzIjoiY2F0YWxvZzpyZWFkIG9yZGVyOnJlYWQgb3JkZXI6d3JpdGUifQ.GUGuavEK1uB8W4KMixbZXAepNkeR7q_I8BjsYQzQKEQ

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 3,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "searchProducts",
    "arguments": { "color": "블랙" }
  }
}


### 12. 외부 MCP 서버 — /sse (docker compose up -d mcp-external-server 후 실행)
GET http://localhost:9090/sse
Accept: text/event-stream

### 13. 외부 MCP 서버 — tools/list (위 #12 응답의 sessionId 복사)
POST http://localhost:9090/mcp/message?sessionId=PASTE_EXTERNAL_SESSION_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 1,
  "method": "tools/list"
}
